{"tha-ap140:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap140:0.2":"Sobhitavagga ","tha-ap140:0.3":"8 Ekapasadaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap140:1.1":"“Narado iti me namam, ","tha-ap140:1.2":"kesavo iti mam vidu; ","tha-ap140:1.3":"Kusalakusalam esam, ","tha-ap140:1.4":"agamam buddhasantikam. ","tha-ap140:2.1":"Mettacitto karuniko, ","tha-ap140:2.2":"atthadassi mahamuni; ","tha-ap140:2.3":"Assasayanto satte so, ","tha-ap140:2.4":"dhammam deseti cakkhuma. ","tha-ap140:3.1":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap140:3.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap140:3.3":"Sattharam abhivadetva, ","tha-ap140:3.4":"pakkamim pacinamukho. ","tha-ap140:4.1":"Sattarase kappasate, ","tha-ap140:4.2":"raja asi mahipati; ","tha-ap140:4.3":"Amittatapano nama, ","tha-ap140:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap140:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap140:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap140:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap140:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekapasadaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap140:7.1":"Ekapasadaniyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}